  <description><![CDATA[<h2>Experience Liguria's most iconic destinations on your summer holiday; from clusters of pastel painted houses in the Cinque Terre to exclusive sea views in the Portofino Natural Park.</h2>
<p>A multi-centre holiday to the <a data-udi="umb://document/79a94ac27eda4c2ea223bc0fe7fd99b6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/79a94ac27eda4c2ea223bc0fe7fd99b6}" title="Cinque Terre">Cinque Terre</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/13b3ee4a5d444c4993a7e2bc1ea88aa2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/13b3ee4a5d444c4993a7e2bc1ea88aa2}" title="Portofino">Portofino</a> areas is a chance to get to know two of the most striking parts of the Italian Riviera. Walk around Portofino harbour, dipping into art galleries and cafés, or head up to the church of St Giorgio and admire its one-of-a-kind church doors. Move on to the Cinque Terre area where you can hit the vineyard-laced walking trails high above the colourful towns, or scope out one of the many castles along the coastline.</p>
<h3>Guide price from: £1,712pp*</h3>
<h3>Your multi-centre holiday options:</h3>
<ul>
<li>7, 10, 11 or 14 nights accommodation in your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Travel on Wednesday or Saturday</li>
</ul>
<h3>Your holiday includes:</h3>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from the UK</li>
<li>Return airport transfers to and from your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Taxi transfers between your chosen destinations</li>
</ul>
