<h2 style="text-align: center;">How to Book Your Multi-Centre Holiday</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>Simply give us a call to book your multi-centre holiday. Flights, hotel and transport? Consider it done. Dial in and let our experts plan your dream getaway. </span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>*Prices are based on 2 people sharing for 4 nights in a Standard Garden View Room at Hotel Regina Elena, Santa Margherita (Portofino area) and 3 nights in a Comfort Room at Hotel Byron, Lerici (Cinque Terre area), with shared transfers between resorts, departing on the 07th June 25 from London Gatwick Airport. Supplements for alternative flights, flight routes, and room types may apply. Prices are correct at the time of publishing on 09/12/24 but are subject to change based on availability. Please call for the most up-to-date pricing and availability before booking.</em></p>]]></description>
