  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<h3>Hotels in the Portofino Area</h3>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/ed859abceb08411c8d08424fa267a79f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ed859abceb08411c8d08424fa267a79f}" title="Grand Hotel Bristol" data-anchor="#">Grand Hotel Bristol Spa Resort</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13092630/erre-spa-indoor-pool.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Grand Hotel Bristol, Portofino" data-udi="umb://media/1bed66c187914685bac4e71c2d34ed02" /></p>
<p>Grand Hotel Bristol Spa Resort stands out on Rapallo's coastline. It's a stunning Art Nouveau building with incredible outside areas and views of the Ligurian Riviera from all around. We love the pool that looks out over the Portofino Promontory. The rooftop a la carte restaurant is a must-try and you can't miss aperitivo in the bar at sunset.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/66bacd322751460c9aa6ea9e112a773c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/66bacd322751460c9aa6ea9e112a773c}" title="Regina Elena Hotel" data-anchor="#">Hotel Regina Elena</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13101470/reginae-14.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Hotel Regina Elena, Portofino" data-udi="umb://media/e8cf39850a7e4eb99608f2f5ebac2e57" /></p>
<p>The Hotel Regina Elena is a family-run hotel and a great base for visiting the surrounding area. The centre of Santa Margherita is just a short walk away and Portofino can be reached by a pleasant coastal walk. This is a charming spot with lots of facilities including a fab rooftop pool with panoramic views.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/a831559a72c34ffdbaecbb24dc01f3fd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a831559a72c34ffdbaecbb24dc01f3fd}" title="Jolanda Hotel" data-anchor="#">Hotel Jolanda</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13090433/hall-d.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Hotel Jolanda, Portofino" data-udi="umb://media/bfca90af3e6d4c5dbf93b05abf1f1f1a" /></p>
<p>Hotel Jolanda offers stylish accommodation. The seafront and the station is just a short walk away from the hotel, making it a great base for exploring Liguria.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/13b3ee4a5d444c4993a7e2bc1ea88aa2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/13b3ee4a5d444c4993a7e2bc1ea88aa2}" title="Portofino" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View all Hotels in the Portofino Area</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></facilityDescription>
  <familyDescription><![CDATA[<h3>Hotels in the Cinque Terre Area</h3>
<h3><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/liguria/cinque-terre/park-hotel-argento" title="Park Hotel Argento">Park Hotel Argento</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13093370/park-hotel-argento-10.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Park Hotel Argento, Cinque Terre" data-udi="umb://media/f98f539e805b416f8b0979dad504781f" /></p>
<p>You'll find the Park Hotel Argento in a quiet area just a few minutes walk away from the centre of Levanto, the beach and the train station. Being able to walk everywhere you need to go, gives you the freedom to experience your holiday on your own terms and easily explore all that the Cinque Terre area has to offer.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/liguria/cinque-terre/park-hotel-argento">Hotel Byron</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13093355/hotel-byron-13.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Hotel Byron, Cinque Terre" data-udi="umb://media/b0375c4dac3f48da93a04a4d3fe868b2" /></p>
<p>Hotel Byron's a newly renovated hotel in a fantastic seaside location just five minutes walk from the centre of Lerici. If you're looking for an action-packed holiday with easy access to walking trails and activities such as tennis, golf and sailing, then this is the perfect hotel for you.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/liguria/cinque-terre/cristallo-park-hotel">Cristallo Park Hotel</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 320px; height: 220px; float: left; margin-right: 15px;" src="/media/13104965/cristallo1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="Cristallo Park, Cinque Terre" data-udi="umb://media/308d9827284d4200a010f9e040ed8d8b" /></p>
<p>Cristallo Park Hotel is a stunning modern hotel and a short walk along the coast to Portovenere town centre. It's in a fantastic location if you want panoramic sea views from your bedroom.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/79a94ac27eda4c2ea223bc0fe7fd99b6" href="/{localLink:umb://document/79a94ac27eda4c2ea223bc0fe7fd99b6}" title="Cinque Terre" class="c-btn c-btn--secondary c-btn c-btn--mid c-btn--secondary-hollow c-btn--wide u-text-center">View all Hotels in the Cinque Terre Area</a></p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call Us to Book Today</a></p>]]></familyDescription>
